Vessel Controller (Finance) - Singapore
Vessel Controller (Finance) - Singapore
Location:  Singapore
Salary:  SGD80000 - SGD160000 per annumVessel Controller (Finance) - Singapore - SG$80,000 - SG$160,000 DOE
An international Shipping company are looking to bring in an experienced Vessel Controller for their Singapore Office,
The successful candidate will be responsible for financial reporting, cash management, variance analysis and auditing.
The ideal candidate will have vast experience in Shipping finance with a few years experience in an assistant managerial role. You must be fluent in Mandarin and English. Finally you must have vast experience but also a high motivation to add value to a new company.
For more information or to apply for this position please contact Tom at Navis Consulting on tom@navis-consulting.com or +44 2392 314 687.
Think Maritime - Think Navis Consulting.
